                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18190217-146-off843 t18190217-146-crimeloc846"></join>. On the 16th of January, in the morning, the carpet was taken from the front of my shop. In the afternoon the prisoner was pointed out to me, and I took him. He said he sold the carpet for 5 s. in Gee's-court. I went, and found it in a cellar there occupied by three sweeps.</p>
